---

title: Cloudburst
layout: post
permalink: /Cloudburst.html
tags: Eric Whitacre, 现代作品

---

<img width="100%" src="http://fmn.rrfmn.com/fmn058/20140701/0845/original_E2XA_70f40000897f125d.jpg" />

<hr style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;" />
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="color:#7f7f7f;">　　《Cloudburst》是埃里克·惠特克（Eric Whitacre）最著名的作品之一。惠特克在1992年完成了这部作品，那年他才22岁。这是一个八声部的合唱作品，使用了钢琴和打击乐伴奏。文字改编自Octavio Paz的诗歌。<br />
    </span>
</p>
<hr style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;" />

<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;text-align:center;">
    <strong><span style="font-size:36px;"></span></strong>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;text-align:center;">
    <strong><span style="font-size:36px;">Cloudburst</span></strong>
</p>

<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    　　<br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    　　1991年，在《Go, Lovely Rose》演出之后，Jocelyn K. Jensen博士找我为她的的高中合唱团写一首曲子。她是一个了不起的指挥，传说能在舞台上做出非常疯狂的事情（舞蹈动作，灯光，服饰等只要你能想到的）。所以我想为她写一个真正能够震撼观众的作品。正好我最近收到了一本精致的 Octavio Paz 诗集。并且大约在同一时间，我见证了一个真实的（也是惊人的）沙漠暴雨。我想这真是老天的安排。
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    　　打响指这玩意（所有的歌手用手指来模拟雨水）是一个古老的篝火游戏，我只是稍加修改。雷霆则是靠着从学校角落里翻出来的巨大铁皮。
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    　　这个作品原本是十分钟左右的时间，但是Jo-Michael Scheibe博士一本正经地说服我“拧紧一点”。我做到了，这个作品（现在是被瘦身成8分半钟），最终在1995年出版。
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<hr style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;" />
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <strong><span style="font-size:18px;color:#595959;">Cloudburst</span></strong>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="color:#595959;font-size:14px;"></span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">The rain…</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Eyes of shadow-water</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">eyes of well-water,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">eyes of dream-water.</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Blue suns, green whirlwinds,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">birdbeaks of light pecking open</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">pomegranate stars.</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">But tell me, burnt earth, is there no water?</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Only blood, only dust,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Only naked footsteps on the thorns?</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">The rain awakens…</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">We must sleep with open eyes,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">we must dream with our hands,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">we must dream the dreams of a river seeking its course,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">of the sun dreaming its worlds,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">we must dream aloud,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">we must sing till the song puts forth roots,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">trunk, branches, birds, stars,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">we must find the lost word,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">and remember what the blood,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">the tides, the earth, and the body say,</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">and return to the point of departure…</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Octavio Paz, 1914-1998</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">(Adapted by Eric Whitacre, Translation by Lysander Kemp)</span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="color:#595959;"><span style="font-size:14px;"></span></span><br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <br />
</p>
<hr style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;" />
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">
    <span style="color:#7f7f7f;">　　<strong><a href="http://t.cn/RvZGEdc" style="color:#7f7f7f;">点击这里</a></strong>可以聆听由Polyphony演唱的《Cloudburst》。这是《Eric Whitacre: Cloudburst and Other Choral Works》这张专辑的第7首作品。</span><br />
</p>
<hr style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;" />
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;text-align:center;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#7f7f7f;">人文爱乐合唱团</span>
</p>
<p>
